column1:
In this part of the study, you will be making a series of monetary decisions.

You will have the choice between taking a gamble,  which will be shown on the left side of the screen, or choosing a sure option, which will be on the right side of the screen. 

For each gamble, you will have a 50% chance of winning money, while the sure option guarantees payoff. 

Press space to continue.

You will have three seconds to make your choice upon seeing the options. 

To choose the gamble, press "1". To choose the sure option, press "2".

You will first be playing some practice rounds. To begin the practice, press enter!
